  + [question_register] is how to emit a branch_refinement_artifact from commit bookends without remote sync
  + [delineation_register] is inside remaining ReadyTaskSet, Task_039, local command, commit bookends, branch artifact record, source evidence, outside, and commit cadence
  + [periphery_register] is remote sync outside, higher-level common repo outside, LM Studio worker authority outside, unrelated dirty files outside, credentials outside, and destructive action outside
