  + [balance_register] is stable because Task_035 completed with tests and outside preserved
  + [integration_register] is Task_035 completed and Task_039 selected as next runtime task
  + [frame_outside] is hidden model state, worker file mutation, remote claims before push, broad local-worker readiness, and unrelated workspace changes

